OL,3,CSouthern Water boss should refuse
OL,4,C'outrageous' pay rise ` Environment
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FThe Environment Secretary has urged
OL,8,FSouthern Water's chief executive to
OL,9,Fturn down a pay rise worth hundreds of
OL,10,Fthousands of pounds, saying it was not
OL,11,F"merited".
OL,13,FLawrence Gosden, who has led Southern
OL,14,FWater since 2022, was awarded #691,000
OL,15,Fas part of a long-term incentive plan
OL,16,Fthis year on top of his fixed pay of
OL,17,F#687,000, according to the company's
OL,18,Fannual report.
