OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FIt is understood that he has only
OL,8,Freceived half of this payment this
OL,9,Fyear, taking his total pay to more
OL,10,Fthan #1 million.
OL,12,FAsked on Sunday about Mr Gosden's pay,
OL,13,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed told
OL,14,Fthe BBC's Sunday With Laura Kuenssberg
OL,15,Fit was "outrageous" and implored
OL,16,FSouthern to "think about how this
OL,17,Flooks to their customers".
