OL,3,CSouthern Water boss should refuse
OL,4,C'outrageous' pay rise ` Environment
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FHe said: "Trust between the customers
OL,8,Fand the water companies is at the
OL,9,Flowest point probably ever, and by
OL,10,Fpaying their senior executives rises
OL,11,Fof that kind, what message are they
OL,12,Fsending to their customers?"
OL,14,FAsked whether Mr Gosden should turn
OL,15,Fdown the pay rise, Mr Reed said: "I
OL,16,Fthink it would be right if he did."
OL,18,FHe added: "I don't think Southern
OL,19,FWater has performed well enough for
OL,20,Fthat kind of pay increase to be
OL,21,Fmerited."
