OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FSouthern Water was banned from paying
OL,8,Fbonuses last month over a so-called
OL,9,F"category 1" sewage spill in the New
OL,10,FForest, Hampshire, in August 2024.
OL,12,FUnder new rules, companies are banned
OL,13,Ffrom paying bonuses if they do not
OL,14,Fmeet environmental, consumer or
OL,15,Ffinancial standards, or are convicted
OL,16,Fof a criminal offence.
