OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FA Southern Water spokesperson said its
OL,8,Fchief executive's pay and benefits
OL,9,Fwere decided by a remuneration
OL,10,Fcommittee "following protocols and
OL,11,Frules set out by Ofwat and in
OL,12,Faccordance with the law".
OL,14,FThey added: "Lawrence Gosden's 2025
OL,15,Fpackage includes a relocation
OL,16,Fallowance, and long-term incentive
OL,17,Fplan paid by shareholders which marks
OL,18,Fimprovements made during the delivery
OL,19,Fof our turnaround plan. Both of these
OL,20,Fpayments represent common industry
OL,21,Fpractice."
