OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FThe review follows widespread
OL,8,Fcriticism of water companies for
OL,9,Fawarding executives large bonuses and
OL,10,Fpaying significant dividends to
OL,11,Fshareholders while missing targets for
OL,12,Finvesting in infrastructure and
OL,13,Foverseeing a rise in sewage pollution
OL,14,Fin England's rivers.
OL,16,FEarlier this month, Southern Water
OL,17,Fitself was forced to ask its owner,
OL,18,FAustralian investment firm Macquarie,
OL,19,Ffor an extra #2.1 billion to help
OL,20,Fboost its struggling finances.
