OL,11,Fone of the most heavily indebted water
OL,12,Ffirms in the UK behind Thames Water,
OL,13,Fpreviously also owned by Macquarie.
OL,15,FA hosepipe ban imposed by Southern
OL,16,FWater comes into effect on Monday.
